Need a licence

You have to reset the visual studio instance or else deleted extencion stuff will be present
c:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio 14.0\VSSDK\VisualStudioIntegration\Tools\Bin> CreateExpInstance /Reset /VSINstance-14.0 /RootSuffix=Exp 

prebuild command 
call "%userprofile%\Documents\Visual Studio 2015\Projects\SSPrototype\SSScripts&Bats\ResetVSInstance.bat"

